dct_title_s: Terrain model of the Gaza Strip and West Bank.
dct_description_sm: Map shows roads, railroads, and built-up areas. Relief shown by shading. Includes relief  elevation profile. "Vertical exaggeration is approximately 3:1." Oriented with north toward upper left. "730856 (E00433) 1-94." "Distance between Tel-Aviv Yafo and Amman is 108 kilometers." "Boundary representation is not necessarily authoritative. The 1950 Israeli proclamation that Jerusalem be the national capital is not recognized by the United States Government."
